8. Model module
---------------
The GModelTemporalPhaseCurve models are now normalised by default unless a
normalize="0" attribute is explicitly added into the XML file. Thus the spectral
component of a sky model with a GModelTemporalPhaseCurve temporal component now
gives the phase-averaged flux (#2154).


9. Numerics module
------------------
None


10. Observation module
----------------------
None


11. Optimization module
-----------------------
None


12. Sky module
--------------
A GSkyRegions::overlaps(GSkyRegions&) method has been added to check the
overlap of any region in a given container with any region in another
container (#1980).

A GSkyMap::overlaps(GSkyRegions&) method has been added to check the overlap
of a sky region with a sky map (#1980).


