20. CTA interface
-----------------
The GCTACubeExposure::fill_cube(), GCTACubePsf::fill_cube(),
GCTACubeEdisp::fill_cube(), and GCTACubeBackground::fill() methods now
exclude any observations from the filling for which the RoI does not
overlap with the cube definition (#1980).


